                                Sadness: </span>
                            <span class="currentValue"
                                style="font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; font-size: xx-large; color: darkgreen;">5</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="uk-width-3-4@s">
                        <label for="slider3" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: x-large;">What is your level of anger
                            at this moment? </label>
                        <input class="uk-input" name="anger_level" type="range" id="slider3" min="0" max="10" step="1"
                            value="5" required>
                        <span>Min: </span>
                        <span class="minValue">0</span>
                        <span>Max: </span>
                        <span class="maxValue">10</span>
                        <div style="text-align: right;">
                            <span
